WEBVTT

00:07:59.104 --> 00:08:02.097
we managed to recruit in our administration

00:08:02.097 --> 00:08:04.092
many young people,

00:08:04.092 --> 00:08:05.954
and we thus managed to build

00:08:05.954 --> 00:08:09.225
a de-politicized public institution

00:08:09.225 --> 00:08:13.745
where men and women were equally represented.

00:08:13.745 --> 00:08:16.287
International organizations

00:08:16.287 --> 00:08:19.665
have invested a lot in Albania during these 20 years,

00:08:19.665 --> 00:08:22.897
not all of it well spent.

00:08:22.897 --> 00:08:26.025
